text: Rosberg is a Swedish surname. It may refer to: * Rosberg racing family ** Keke Rosberg, father of Nico, former Finnish Formula One racing driver and 1982 World Champion ** Nico Rosberg, son of Keke, former German Formula One racing driver and 2016 World Champion * Christer Rosberg, Swedish soccer player * Marit Røsberg Jacobsen (born 1994) Norwegian handball player ==References== ==See also== * Team Rosberg, a racing team owned by the Rosberg racing family Category:Surnames of Swedish origin
